{"tid":2164510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"垃圾喇沙仔已敗走美國, 人生已完 [FCed有圖]","createTime":"2020-08-19T08:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T08:55:20.000Z","uid":22839,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60130db4f195d6686d6366e08272db5036fb8840","tid":2164510,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"新任警務處處長盧偉聰接棒，外界對其身世甚感興趣。原來他除以優異成績入讀傳統名校喇沙書院，當時在校內更是小飛魚，奪魁無數，而且品學兼優，歷任班長。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰曾在警隊首長級蛙泳賽中，連奪五連冠。這名警隊「飛魚」在中學時代已是游泳健將，本身是喇沙泳隊隊員，不時在校內獲取獎項。該校副校長鄧仲翩更細訴盧偉聰中六時曾奪水運會總冠軍，其照片至今仍保存於喇沙書院的檔案室內。<br />\n<br />\n副校長又表示，盧當年在校內成績優異，加上品行良好，多年來一直獲任命為班長，每次拍攝班相時，都坐在班主任旁邊的重要位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HapVsH0GKIrtsKSUU_o0eg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/_2015050415395270554_popup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHapVsH0GKIrtsKSUU_o0eg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F_2015050415395270554_popup.jpg&h=c212fc6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">盧偉聰中六時奪水運會冠軍。（資料圖片）</span>"},{"pid":"8b31659d01df1123f403575e9df44c82a84cbb87","tid":2164510,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"後生果時咁瘦，依家咁肥"},{"pid":"6e9b4812aa8edb825e8c6eff24e01426cd35c84a","tid":2164510,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b31659d01df1123f403575e9df44c82a84cbb87","tid":2164510,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"後生果時咁瘦，依家咁肥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:46:55.000Z","msg":"啲高官肚滿腸肥正路啦"},{"pid":"4504664e86061489d79880e6a1a28c6456877a7b","tid":2164510,"uid":275213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"以為嗰個喇沙仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}